# IOS (read AGENTS.md first)

- **Max 3 files** per task. No repo-wide search unless user asks.
- **Data path:** `service.ts` → `v1Client` → `/api/v1`. No `getSupabase().from/rpc` in pages/components/hooks (auth OK).
- **New endpoint:** handler → `v1Router.ts` → v1Client → service.
- **Never open:** `docs/`, `supabase/migrations/`, `node_modules/`, `dist/`, `package-lock.json`, `src/lib/academy/content/`.
